# Personal Preferences

## Typescript

- Never use `any` unless absolutely required. Less strict in unit tests about this.

## Commands

- Dont run the dev server or any command that are probably already running as a watcher just assume it is.
- Prefer check/linting commands e.g. `npm run lint` etc

## Workflow

- If asked to do to much work at once stop and state that clearly.
